=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::GestureClick
=head1 Description

B<Gnome::Gtk4::GestureClick> is a L<Gnome::Gtk4::Gesture|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/Gesture> implementation for clicks.

It is able to recognize multiple clicks on a nearby zone, which
can be listened for through the I<pressed>
signal. Whenever time or distance between clicks exceed the GTK
defaults, I<stopped> is emitted, and the
click counter is reset.

