=head1 Signals

=comment -----------------------------------------------------------------------
=head3 pressed

Emitted whenever a button or touch press happens.

=begin code
method handler (
  gint $n-press,
  gdouble $x,
  gdouble $y,
  Int :$_handle_id,
  N-GObject :$_native-object,
  Gnome::Gtk4::GestureClick :$_widget,
  *%user-options
)
=end code

=item $n-press; how many touch/button presses happened with this one.
=item $x; The X coordinate, in widget allocation coordinates.
=item $y; The Y coordinate, in widget allocation coordinates.
=item $_handle_id; The registered event handler id.
=item $_native-object; The native object provided by the Raku object which registered this event. This is a native B<Gnome::Gtk4::GestureClick> object.
=item %user-options; A list of named arguments provided by L<.register-signal() in class Object|/content-docs/api2/reference/GObject/Object#register-signal>.

